# --- Backend API origin ---
# VITE_BACKEND_URL: origin backend (Railway) untuk build PRODUCTION.
# - TANPA trailing slash, TANPA "/api" (path "/api" & "/sanctum" ditambahkan oleh kode).
# - Contoh: https://careerflow-api.up.railway.app
# - DEV: biarkan kosong / hapus — request relatif akan diteruskan Vite proxy
#   (lihat vite.config.js) ke http://localhost:8000.
# Catatan: di Vercel, set variabel ini di Project Settings -> Environment Variables.
VITE_BACKEND_URL=
